{
  "stem": "21817.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there was a famous theater.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to come from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What's the name?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a Yiddish theater.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly what.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But once in awhile because there was a big Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I would say maybe 50% or more, were Jews in Mlawa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And also there's one famous Jewish writer, Opatoshu.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was born in Mlawa.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But this-- all this happened before my time, but they were talking always about him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were lots of organizations, Zionist organization, Bund organization.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were some also extreme left organization, like a communist party, whatever they-- because when they had the war in Spain, the Civil War, I remember my dad told me that some, some of the people went to fight even in Spain.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not-- there were a few, a few young men, volunteered to fight in Spain.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish men, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I just know from what my father told me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've never heard that before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also there were some Christian also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There must have been a communist-- I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't say it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I know that some of the people went to fight in Spain, young men.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, there were Americans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were called the Lincoln Brigade.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was the same idea, that--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was  an international brigade.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we did not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All I know it is from my father told us, I think, once at a dinner time, that certain people, which he know about it, went to Spain.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, I would say, approximately 25% or 30% of Polish citizen were German descent.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're called volksdeutsche.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
